cts on public opinion about climate policy.Populist discourse per se is not an obstacle to adopting ambitious climate policy in the {US}.Political entrepreneurs can foster support for climate policies by emphasizing elite responsiveness to citizens’ needs and preferences.Populist attacks on established elites are unlikely to derail support for climate policy.},
